      "id": "69f7bc7da1acd68ba5ba6784",
      "text": "2026/03/27―Mijikko",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777843326,
      "updated": 1777843326
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bc7e0000000000422f6b",
      "text": "from [2026/03/27]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777843326,
      "updated": 1777843326
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bc7e0000000000422f6c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777843326,
      "updated": 1777843329
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bc7e0000000000422f6d",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777843326,
      "updated": 1777843326
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bc7e0000000000422f6e",
      "text": "　[ギルティ炭酸]の反応見てると「クソ[まずい]」と「クソ[うまい]」の二択に別れてるの笑う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777843326,
      "updated": 1777843326
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bc7e0000000000422f6f",
      "text": "　　[Mijikko.icon]は追加で2本買った",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777843326,
      "updated": 1777843326
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bc7e0000000000422f70",
      "text": "　　[カロリーデカい]からか作業中はガブガブ飲んじゃうな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777843326,
      "updated": 1777843326
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bc7e0000000000422f71",
      "text": "　[アーティスト]が[嘘をついてはいけない]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777843326,
      "updated": 1777843326
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bc7e0000000000422f72",
      "text": "　　だってそれを見る人は正当に評価する権利があるから",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777843326,
      "updated": 1777843326
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bc7e0000000000422f73",
      "text": "　　そう言って[Mijikko.icon]は[嘘だらけのアート]を作りました",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777843326,
      "updated": 1777843326
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7bc7e0000000000422f74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777843326,
